name: BostonBike
0:
”Alexa, open Boston Bike”
”Alexa, ask Boston Bike for the nearest station”
”Alexa, ask Boston Bike for the closest bikes”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: boston bike
des:
Boston Bike will find the closest Hubway Bike Rental stations and tell you the location and availability of bikes and docks.

Say "Alexa, open Boston Bike" or "Alexa, ask Boston Bike for the nearest bike"
